WEBVTT

00:00.967 --> 00:02.568
<i>Previously on</i> Gotham:

00:02.570 --> 00:03.635
(grunts)

00:03.637 --> 00:05.270
BULLOCK:
<i>The guys call him the Ogre.</i>

00:05.272 --> 00:06.905
<i>He's a serial killer.</i>

00:06.907 --> 00:09.541
Whoever did this is a monster.

00:09.543 --> 00:12.211
The blood of his next victim
is on my hands.

00:12.213 --> 00:14.113
If you don't drop it,
that blood could be Lee's.

00:14.115 --> 00:16.382
<i>Because the Ogre
retaliates against any cop</i>

00:16.384 --> 00:19.184
<i>who investigates and kills
the people they love.</i>

00:19.186 --> 00:20.853
BRUCE: <i>The man who stabbed
Alfred, he's in Gotham.</i>

00:20.855 --> 00:22.287
You need
my help to find him.

00:22.289 --> 00:24.023
Who sent you?

00:24.025 --> 00:27.026
You want me to tell Bunderslaw
that you're onto him?

00:27.028 --> 00:28.427
(screaming)

00:31.598 --> 00:34.133
(train clacking, bell clangs,
ship's horn toots)

00:36.669 --> 00:38.737
(car horns honk,
siren wails in distance)

00:42.609 --> 00:44.977
Hey!

00:47.047 --> 00:49.081
You look far from home.

00:50.683 --> 00:52.584
Get away from him.

00:52.586 --> 00:54.253
Or what?

00:55.488 --> 00:57.489
(scoffs)

00:57.491 --> 00:59.558
Whatever.

01:04.497 --> 01:05.864
SELINA: Come on.

01:05.866 --> 01:07.166
Did you go back?

01:07.168 --> 01:09.234
Yeah.
The cops are there.

01:10.537 --> 01:12.538
And?

01:12.540 --> 01:14.039
And?

01:14.041 --> 01:15.974
What do you think?

01:15.976 --> 01:18.710
He fell out of
a five-story window. He's dead.

01:20.313 --> 01:21.880
(voice breaks):
Why'd you do it?

01:21.882 --> 01:24.283
He told us what we wanted.
He told us about Bunderslaw.

01:24.285 --> 01:25.417
You didn't have to go
and kill the guy!

01:25.419 --> 01:26.952
Yes, I did!
'Cause the moment we'd left,

01:26.954 --> 01:28.320
he was gonna go tell his boss!

01:28.322 --> 01:30.622
Who works for you,
by the way.

01:30.624 --> 01:32.524
He's the one who
tried to kill me,

01:32.526 --> 01:35.427
who tried to kill your butler...

01:35.429 --> 01:37.696
who probably
killed your parents.

01:37.698 --> 01:41.233
I saved your life.

01:41.235 --> 01:44.069
Besides... you wanted
to do it, too.

01:44.071 --> 01:46.472
You just didn't
have the guts.

01:48.441 --> 01:50.542
Wait...!
Just go home.

01:50.544 --> 01:52.711
We still have to find out who
Bunderslaw is and what he wants.

01:52.713 --> 01:54.179
You mean you do.

01:54.181 --> 01:55.981
You really think this is over?

01:55.983 --> 01:58.217
He's gonna come after us.

01:59.385 --> 02:01.820
So what's next? Hmm?

02:05.558 --> 02:07.059
His safe.

02:07.061 --> 02:08.327
What?

02:08.329 --> 02:09.862
Every senior executive
at Wayne Enterprises

02:09.864 --> 02:11.263
has a safe in their office.

02:11.265 --> 02:14.133
A-Any secrets Bunderslaw has,
that's where they'll be.

02:14.135 --> 02:15.634
Key or combination?

02:15.636 --> 02:18.270
Key. My dad had one.

02:18.272 --> 02:21.473
He'll probably
keep it on him, then.

02:22.742 --> 02:25.210
Figure out a way to get
me close, and I'll steal it.

02:25.212 --> 02:26.712
Can you do that?

02:26.714 --> 02:27.980
I think so.

02:27.982 --> 02:29.448
And what happened tonight,

02:29.450 --> 02:32.284
you tell no one.

02:32.286 --> 02:34.620
Not your buddy
Detective Gordon,

02:34.622 --> 02:36.622
not your butler.

02:36.624 --> 02:38.690
No one.

